graph LR
    Kubeflow[Kubeflow Notebook Controller]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Kubeflow -->|cluster runtime| K8s[Kubernetes 1.22.0+<br/>Required]
    Kubeflow -->|controller framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime 0.8.0+<br/>Required]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Kubeflow -.->|VirtualService routing| Istio[Istio v1alpha3<br/>Optional]
    Kubeflow -.->|metrics monitoring| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Optional]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Kubeflow -->|receives Notebook CRs| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>jupyter-web-app]
    Kubeflow -->|routes via| IstioGateway[Istio Gateway<br/>kubeflow/kubeflow-gateway]
    Kubeflow -->|pulls images| ImageRegistry[Container Image Registry<br/>Jupyter images]

    %% Integration Points
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|can create| Kubeflow
    Workbench[Workbench Deployments] -.->|notebook pods| Kubeflow

    %% External Services
    Kubeflow -->|API operations| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    Kubeflow -->|queries activity| NotebookPods[Notebook Pods<br/>8888/TCP HTTP]

    %% API Group Dependencies
    Kubeflow -->|watches/manages| NotebookCRD[CRD: kubeflow.org/v1/Notebook]
    Kubeflow -->|creates| StatefulSetAPI[API: apps/v1/StatefulSet]
    Kubeflow -->|creates| ServiceAPI[API: core/v1/Service]
    Kubeflow -.->|creates optional| VirtualServiceAPI[API: networking.istio.io/v1alpha3/VirtualService]

